title: Noctes ambrosianae,
author: Wilson, John
snippet: || The Fruid s fu o sma troots, and I sune had a string.

title: Noctes ambrosianae,
author: Wilson, John
snippet: Sae I just thocht I wad try the Fruid wi the flee, and put on a pro fessor.

title: Noctes ambrosianae,
author: Wilson, John
snippet: But I forgot I wasna on foot the beast gotblawn, and coming up the Fruid, reested wi me on Garlet-Dod.
